description: FIRST TIME EVER ON THE MARKET! This south-facing home is located on the 20th floor and is truly one-of-a-kind!, This unique home features a spacious kitchen with space to add a floating island, custom Italian, lacquered finish cabinets and matching caesarstone backsplash.  Bird’s eye view of the grand pool from the living room floor to ceiling windows.  EchelonSeaport features the most abundant amenities in all of Boston including: 24/7 concierge, doormen, porters, three swimming pools, grilling areas and outdoor dining space, resident sky lounges, fitness center with mind/body studio and pilates equipment, weekly fitness programming and resident events.
